{"sections":{"main":{"type":"main-page","disabled":true,"settings":{"show_page_title":true,"heading_size":"h2","title_alignment":"center","heading_size_info":"h4","section_width":"narrow","spacing_top":"2","spacing_bottom":"2","section_border":"none"}},"4a4e5c1e-f0c1-4eff-a176-be471c0b1ef5":{"type":"hero-alt","blocks":{"template--19560386036027__4a4e5c1e-f0c1-4eff-a176-be471c0b1ef5-168690527864b2abdd-0":{"type":"text","settings":{"subtitle":"Our Mission","title":"Sahara Values","content":"<p>From transparency in supply and design, our business ethics, innovation and our workplace culture, find out what's important to us at FAE. Our mission is set on a future of innovation and inclusivity with minimal impact on the planet, while simultaneously empowering all people who come in contact with <a href=\"https:\/\/www.fae.house\/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/www.fae.house\/\">FAE<\/a>.<\/p>","button_style":"button--filled","button_text":"View more","button_url":"\/","button_separator":true}},"template--19560386036027__4a4e5c1e-f0c1-4eff-a176-be471c0b1ef5-168690527864b2abdd-1":{"type":"media","settings":{}}},"block_order":["template--19560386036027__4a4e5c1e-f0c1-4eff-a176-be471c0b1ef5-168690527864b2abdd-0","template--19560386036027__4a4e5c1e-f0c1-4eff-a176-be471c0b1ef5-168690527864b2abdd-1"],"settings":{"hero_alt_banner_height":50,"section_width":"page","color_scheme":"scheme-3","spacing_top":"2","spacing_bottom":"2","section_border":"none"}},"53702f4d-1baa-4c59-ba17-fd7384db5269":{"type":"dual-tiles","blocks":{"template--19560386036027__53702f4d-1baa-4c59-ba17-fd7384db5269-168690528514c33e48-0":{"type":"tile","settings":{"show_on":"both","media_position":"top","heading_size":"h2","button_style":"button--outlined-inverse","button_separator":false,"content_position":"justify-center","content_alignment":"text-center align-center","desktop_aspect_ratio":"3\/4","content_position_mobile":"justify-center--mobile","content_alignment_mobile":"text-center--mobile align-center--mobile","mobile_aspect_ratio":"1\/1","video_mobile_compact":false}},"template--19560386036027__53702f4d-1baa-4c59-ba17-fd7384db5269-168690528514c33e48-1":{"type":"tile","settings":{"show_on":"both","color_scheme":"scheme-3","media_position":"top","heading_size":"h2","text":"<p>FAE is proud to be working with i=change donating $1 of every sale to one of the three charities, chosen by our customers at the checkout. i=change allows for us to uphold our commitment to a fair and more sustainable future, everyday. <\/p><p>Our Charities:<\/p><p>- CLEAN THE SEA<br\/>- PROTECT A WOMAN<br\/>- SUPPORT MENTAL HEALTH<\/p>","button_text":"Explore","button_style":"button--filled","button_separator":false,"content_position":"justify-center","content_alignment":"text-center align-center","desktop_aspect_ratio":"3\/4","content_position_mobile":"justify-center--mobile","content_alignment_mobile":"text-center--mobile align-center--mobile","mobile_aspect_ratio":"3\/4","video_mobile_compact":false}}},"block_order":["template--19560386036027__53702f4d-1baa-4c59-ba17-fd7384db5269-168690528514c33e48-0","template--19560386036027__53702f4d-1baa-4c59-ba17-fd7384db5269-168690528514c33e48-1"],"settings":{"block_size":"half","gap_between_tiles":"4","gap_between_tiles_mobile":"2","reverse_on_mobile":false,"section_width":"page","color_scheme":"scheme-1","spacing_top":"4","spacing_bottom":"2","section_border":"none"}},"3209e946-061c-496b-86e8-04dd9020ef6b":{"type":"dual-tiles","blocks":{"23ed6188-851e-4bee-ba80-fe7bca888f89":{"type":"tile","settings":{"show_on":"both","color_scheme":"scheme-3","media_position":"top","heading":"Our Factory","heading_size":"h5","text":"<p>At FAE we aspire to be thoughtful across every step of the way. Our team in Bali is more than just a factory, its a family that has supported the growth of FAE to make it what it is today. We want to make sure that at all stages we are creating a positive impact on th lives of the people who make our swimwear.<\/p>","button_url":"\/","button_style":"button--filled","button_separator":false,"content_position":"justify-center","content_alignment":"text-center align-center","desktop_aspect_ratio":"3\/4","content_position_mobile":"justify-center--mobile","content_alignment_mobile":"text-center--mobile align-center--mobile","mobile_aspect_ratio":"3\/4","video_mobile_compact":false}},"455295e0-052a-42dc-8186-af0307d59a16":{"type":"tile","settings":{"show_on":"both","media_position":"top","heading_size":"h2","button_style":"button--outlined-inverse","button_separator":false,"content_position":"justify-center","content_alignment":"text-center align-center","desktop_aspect_ratio":"3\/4","content_position_mobile":"justify-center--mobile","content_alignment_mobile":"text-center--mobile align-center--mobile","mobile_aspect_ratio":"1\/1","video_mobile_compact":false}}},"block_order":["23ed6188-851e-4bee-ba80-fe7bca888f89","455295e0-052a-42dc-8186-af0307d59a16"],"settings":{"block_size":"half","gap_between_tiles":"4","gap_between_tiles_mobile":"2","reverse_on_mobile":false,"section_width":"max-w-page","spacing_top":"2","spacing_bottom":"4","section_border":"none"}},"213c6866-ea59-4d8a-a4d6-0dc8c0a4b617":{"type":"hero-alt","blocks":{"template--19560386036027__213c6866-ea59-4d8a-a4d6-0dc8c0a4b617-168690527864b2abdd-0":{"type":"text","settings":{"title":"Our Employees","content":"<ul><li>All employees in Bali received well above the minimum wage with 13 months salary a year. They receive two months' wages for a vacation of up to 25 days.<\/li><li>Our factory provides free medical insurance to all their employees, including their spouses and children, covering doctor's fees, prescription medications & hospitalisation. <\/li><li>Every lunch break, our factory provides a glass of fresh juice, a hot cooked meal and vitamin supplements. <\/li><\/ul>","button_style":"button--filled","button_text":"View more","button_url":"\/","button_separator":true}},"template--19560386036027__213c6866-ea59-4d8a-a4d6-0dc8c0a4